<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ر وأ:</span> <span class="c2">(رَوَّأَ)</span> فِي الْأَمْرِ <span class="c2">(تَرْوِئَةً)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(تَرْوِيئًا)</span> بِالْمَدِّ نَظَرَ فِيهِ وَلَمْ يُعَجِّلْ، وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الرَّوِيَّةُ)</span> تَرَكُوا هَمَزَهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رُوَاءٌ فِي رَأَى وَفِي رَوَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>